('95734','33021','5','Luxury villa with stunning sea views in Son Vida'),
('95735','33022','5','Son Vida is located just 3 km from Palma de Mallorca and is one of the luxury residential areas in Mallorca. In the immediate vicinity there are 3 golf courses and two 5 star hotels.\r\nThe villa stands on over 2,000m² plot with fantastic panoramic views of the city of Palma and the sea. The approximately 900m² living space is spread over the main house and a separate guest apartment (currently 80m² office and conference room) as well as a gym and a charming wine cellar. All rooms have sea views and are equipped with high-quality materials, such as marble floors, underfloor heating (oil / water), air conditioning, lift, alarm system with cameras interior and exterior and many more. The villa is in good condition and will be sold partly furnished. About the generously proportioned entrance hall on the upper floor you can reach the living room with fireplace and covered terrace, a kitchen with access to the barbecue area, a master bedroom with lounge, bathroom and dressing room, access to the garage, guest toilet and a utility room. On the lower floor (pool level) are 3 further bedrooms with a bathroom en suite, a meditation room (japaneese style) and a sauna with outdoor located Jacuzzi. A pool with open and covered sun terraces completes the offer. Top Villa - Top location - Super Price !!\r\n'),
